- DIDN'T YOU GET ENOUGH?

00:58.226 --> 00:59.686
- NEVER ENOUGH.

00:59.727 --> 01:01.397
- WHY DON'T WE SAVE IT
TILL THE WEEKEND?

01:01.429 --> 01:03.859
- WHY DON'T WE SAVE IT
TILL WE GET TO THE CAR?

01:03.897 --> 01:06.197
- I WAS THINKING...

01:06.234 --> 01:07.874
THAT WE COULD GO AWAY,
JUST THE TWO OF US.

01:07.901 --> 01:09.441
SNOWBOARDING.

01:09.470 --> 01:11.270
- COOL, EXCEPT THERE'S NO SNOW.

01:11.305 --> 01:13.135
- IN VERMONT.

01:13.174 --> 01:14.444
DAPHNE WAS JUST THERE
WITH HER BOYFRIEND.

01:14.475 --> 01:15.775
SHE SAID IT WAS AMAZING.

01:15.809 --> 01:17.249
THEY STAYED IN THIS
AWESOME PLACE.

01:17.278 --> 01:18.508
IT WAS A CONVERTED FARMHOUSE,

01:18.546 --> 01:20.646
AND EVERY ROOM HAD
A FIREPLACE AND A JACUZZI.

01:20.681 --> 01:23.381
- DID THEY HAVE THOSE LITTLE
MINTS ON THE PILLOWS?

01:23.417 --> 01:25.247
- I FORGOT, BRIAN KINNEY
DOESN'T DO ROMANCE.

01:25.286 --> 01:26.686
- I DON'T NEED AN EXCUSE
TO FUCK.

01:26.720 --> 01:29.690
- YOU ALSO DON'T NEED
AN EXCUSE TO TURN ME DOWN.

01:29.723 --> 01:31.193
WHY DON'T YOU JUST ADMIT

01:31.225 --> 01:34.425
YOU DON'T WANT TO GO AWAY
WITH ME FOR THE WEEKEND?

01:34.462 --> 01:38.232
- I DON'T WANT TO GO AWAY
WITH YOU FOR THE WEEKEND.

01:38.266 --> 01:39.766
- WELL, AT LEAST IT'S OUT
IN THE OPEN.

01:39.800 --> 01:41.640
- I WANT TO GO AWAY WITH YOU
FOR THE WHOLE FUCKING WEEK.

01:41.669 --> 01:42.899
- RIGHT.

01:42.936 --> 01:44.606
- HEY, IF YOU'RE
NOT INTERESTED,

01:44.638 --> 01:47.608
I CAN FIND SOMEBODY WHO IS.

01:47.641 --> 01:49.211
A WEEK WITH ME IN VERMONT?

01:49.243 --> 01:52.313
JACUZZI, FIREPLACE?

01:52.346 --> 01:55.446
GUESS IT'S JUST THE TWO OF US.

01:55.483 --> 01:56.623
- ARE YOU SERIOUS?

01:56.650 --> 01:57.790
- YOU'RE OFF ON SPRING BREAK.

01:57.818 --> 01:59.248
I'M ABOUT TO MAKE PARTNER,

01:59.287 --> 02:01.187
WHICH I'D SAY
MORE THAN ENTITLES ME

02:01.222 --> 02:03.362
TO A WEEK OF SNOWBOARDING

02:03.391 --> 02:04.731
AND FUCKING YOUR BRAINS OUT.

02:04.758 --> 02:07.198
- REALLY?

02:15.869 --> 02:17.769
- DID YOU PUT GUS DOWN?

02:17.805 --> 02:22.505
- YEP, HE'S ALL
SNUGGLED UP IN HIS BED.

02:22.543 --> 02:24.713
NOW IT'S MY TURN.

02:27.548 --> 02:29.218
- OH, POOR BABY.

02:29.250 --> 02:30.780
YOU LOOK EXHAUSTED.

02:30.818 --> 02:32.588
- SO DO YOU.

02:34.955 --> 02:36.515
- ROLL OVER.

02:36.557 --> 02:38.187
- WHAT FOR?

02:38.226 --> 02:40.926
- GO AHEAD.
COME ON.

02:40.961 --> 02:42.261
- AHH!
WHOO.

02:42.296 --> 02:43.256
- FACE DOWN.

02:43.297 --> 02:44.667
- OOH, YES, SIR.
MA'AM.

02:44.698 --> 02:46.768
[giggling]

02:51.472 --> 02:54.942
- AH, YOU ARE GOING
TO LOVE THIS.

02:54.975 --> 02:58.675
- [sigh of contentment]

02:58.712 --> 02:59.712
- THAT'S IT.

02:59.747 --> 03:02.277
- THAT FEELS GOOD.

03:02.316 --> 03:04.586
- LET ALL THE TENSION GO.

03:06.320 --> 03:07.290
[door opens]

03:07.321 --> 03:08.391
- JUST FINISHED THE FLOORS.

03:08.422 --> 03:09.892
THEY LOOK GREAT.

03:09.923 --> 03:11.693
- THAT'S NICE.

03:11.725 --> 03:12.785
- 'NIGHT.

03:12.826 --> 03:16.326
- 'NIGHT.

03:16.364 --> 03:18.274
MAYBE I SHOULD'VE GONE
WITH THE HARDWOOD

03:18.299 --> 03:19.399
INSTEAD OF THE PINE.

03:19.433 --> 03:22.243
- DON'T THINK ABOUT IT.
JUST RELAX.

03:32.380 --> 03:34.620
NOW ROLL OVER.

03:39.687 --> 03:43.517
THIS IS A SPECIAL FORM
OF MASSAGE...

03:45.826 --> 03:48.296
CALLED FOREPLAY.

03:57.037 --> 03:59.367
- OH, I'VE MISSED THIS.

03:59.407 --> 04:01.807
- ME TOO.

04:04.445 --> 04:07.045
GOD, YOU'RE SO HOT.

04:07.080 --> 04:09.950
- [stifled yawn]

04:09.983 --> 04:12.523
OH, SO ARE YOU.

04:40.914 --> 04:42.084
- YOU KNOW,
THE GOOD THING

04:42.115 --> 04:43.515
ABOUT NOT BALANCING
YOUR CHECK BOOK

04:43.551 --> 04:44.691
IS THAT WHEN YOU FINALLY DO,

04:44.718 --> 04:45.948
YOU GET TO RELIVE
ALL YOUR PURCHASES.

04:45.986 --> 04:47.916
OOH, THE PLEASURE VAULT.

04:47.955 --> 04:51.055
- ALL RIGHT, LET ME SEE.

04:51.091 --> 04:52.661
- NO, NO.

04:52.693 --> 04:54.033
ALL RIGHT, YOU KNOW,

04:54.061 --> 04:58.371
IN THE FUTURE,
BALANCE BEFORE YOU BUY.

04:58.399 --> 05:00.469
HOW MUCH IS IT GONNA COST ME
THIS TIME?

05:00.501 --> 05:01.771
- UM, 50?

05:01.802 --> 05:04.412
- YEAH, UH, CLOSER TO 80,

05:04.438 --> 05:05.768
IF I WANT TO TURN
MY PHONE BACK ON.

05:05.806 --> 05:07.676
- TRY 100 IF YOU'D LIKE
TO PAY HALF THE ELECTRIC.

05:12.846 --> 05:14.816
- SO IS HE AS GOOD
AS HE LOOKS?

05:14.848 --> 05:17.418
AND SPARE US
YOUR MONOSYLLABIC ANSWERS.

05:17.451 --> 05:18.751
I WANT DETAILS.

05:18.786 --> 05:21.586
- FIRST I MADE HIM
WORSHIP MY COCK FOR AN HOUR.

05:21.622 --> 05:25.092
THEN I LET HIM RIM ME
FOR A GOOD 45 MINUTES,

05:25.125 --> 05:27.625
