SO HARD HE PASSED OUT.

05:27.661 --> 05:29.131
I'M SURPRISED HE'S UP
AND WALKING AROUND.

05:29.162 --> 05:31.702
- OOH, CAN THE SEX TALK.
LESBIAN APPROACHING.

05:31.732 --> 05:33.072
- HMM, YOU KIDDING?

