OF FOUL-MOUTHED FAGS.

05:41.141 --> 05:43.081
- WELL, SOMEBODY'S
ON THE RAG.

05:43.110 --> 05:44.850
- OR NOT GETTING ANY.

05:44.878 --> 05:46.608
- YOU SEE HOW MUCH YOU GET WHEN
YOU HAVE A FAMILY TO SUPPORT,

05:46.647 --> 05:48.717
A KID TO RAISE,
AND A MAJOR RENOVATION GOING ON

05:48.749 --> 05:50.019
UNDER YOUR ROOF.

05:50.050 --> 05:51.650
BUT OF COURSE YOU NEVER WILL

05:51.685 --> 05:54.455
SINCE YOUR ONLY RESPONSIBILITY
IS TO YOUR DICKS.

05:54.488 --> 05:56.088
- WHICH IS WHY I'M SMILING,
AND YOU'RE NOT.

05:56.123 --> 05:59.463
- SOUNDS TO ME LIKE
A CASE OF L.B.D.

05:59.493 --> 06:02.163
- DUN-DUN-DUN!

06:02.195 --> 06:04.125
- WHAT THE HELL'S THAT?
- LESBIAN BED DEATH.

06:04.164 --> 06:05.874
- YOU KNOW, FIRST IT DRIES UP,

06:05.899 --> 06:07.739
THEN IT SHRIVELS UP,
THEN IT CLOSES UP,

06:07.768 --> 06:09.168
THEN IT DISAPPEARS.

06:09.202 --> 06:10.372
