HEARD OF THIS?

06:10.404 --> 06:13.744
- BECAUSE IT ONLY EXISTS IN
THE MINDS OF CUNTY GAY MEN.

06:13.774 --> 06:15.014
- REOW!

06:15.042 --> 06:16.612
- DON'T WORRY, MEL,
THEY'RE DOING RESEARCH.

06:16.644 --> 06:18.114
NEW DEVELOPMENTS
ARE EMERGING EVERY DAY.

06:18.145 --> 06:19.875
- THERE'S GOING TO BE
A TELETHON.

06:19.913 --> 06:21.483
