UNTIL I DROP.

07:18.271 --> 07:20.941
POP!
OH.

07:20.974 --> 07:22.244
- CONGRATULATIONS.

07:22.275 --> 07:24.005
- THANK YOU.
- WHAT ABOUT ME?

07:27.014 --> 07:28.824
YOU MADE ME A PROMISE.

07:28.849 --> 07:30.579
IF WE HAD ANOTHER
5 MILLION-PLUS YEAR--

07:30.618 --> 07:32.618
- LOOK, I HAD NO CHOICE.

07:32.653 --> 07:34.053
