07:46.734 --> 07:48.044
I GIVE YOU MY WORD.

07:48.068 --> 07:49.698
- [scoffs]

07:56.744 --> 07:59.154
- WELL, WITH THE MONEY
TEDDY LOANED ME,

07:59.179 --> 08:04.179
