SHOULD BE $147.16.

08:04.217 --> 08:07.887
- SO WERE YOUR
CALCULATIONS ACCURATE?

08:07.921 --> 08:11.091
- JUST A SMIDGE OFF.

08:11.124 --> 08:14.964
