$10,000,147.16.

08:14.995 --> 08:19.665
- HUH?

08:19.700 --> 08:21.540
OBVIOUSLY THAT'S A MISTAKE.

08:21.569 --> 08:22.569
- NOT NECESSARILY.

08:22.603 --> 08:26.113
IT IS AN INTEREST-BEARING
ACCOUNT.

08:26.139 --> 08:27.579
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

08:27.608 --> 08:29.908
- ONLY ONE WAY TO FIND OUT.

08:39.653 --> 08:42.293
[chuckles]

08:42.322 --> 08:43.962
- LESBIAN BED DEATH?

08:43.991 --> 08:45.691
WHAT KIND OF BULLSHIT
IS THAT?

08:45.726 --> 08:47.086
- THERE MUST BE
SOMETHING TO IT.

08:47.127 --> 08:48.657
I MEAN, WE KNOW AT LEAST
THREE OTHER COUPLES

08:48.696 --> 08:50.096
WHO HAVE STOPPED HAVING SEX.

08:50.130 --> 08:53.100
- EVERY COUPLE GOES THROUGH
HOT AND COLD SPELLS.

08:53.133 --> 08:54.703
HOW LONG HAVE YOU BEEN
TOGETHER?

08:54.735 --> 08:55.795
- SEVEN YEARS.

08:55.836 --> 08:57.836
- I'D CONSIDER YOURSELVES
LUCKY.

08:57.871 --> 08:59.311
LISTEN, I MAY NOT BE
AN AUTHORITY

08:59.339 --> 09:01.109
ON LONG-TERM RELATIONSHIPS.

09:01.141 --> 09:03.641
