IT JUST NEEDS RECHARGING.

09:10.784 --> 09:13.654
WHAT YOU NEED
IS TO SHAKE THINGS UP.

09:13.687 --> 09:15.917
DO SOMETHING DIFFERENT,
BE SPONTANEOUS.

09:15.956 --> 09:17.956
- SPONTANEOUS.

09:17.991 --> 09:20.161
- YEAH.

09:20.193 --> 09:23.603
A COUPLE OF FUCKABLE BABES
LIKE YOU?

09:23.631 --> 09:26.801
