HAVE ANY PROBLEM.

09:38.411 --> 09:42.251
- I FOUND THIS GAY B & B
FIVE MINUTES FROM SUGARBUSH.

09:42.282 --> 09:44.622
- SOUNDS SUSPICIOUSLY LESBIAN.

09:44.652 --> 09:46.122
- IT'S THE BEST SNOWBOARDING
IN VERMONT.

09:46.153 --> 09:47.993
- UH-HUH.

09:48.021 --> 09:50.321
- THIS IS THE FIRST TIME THAT
WE'VE EVER GONE AWAY TOGETHER.

09:50.357 --> 09:51.727
- IS THAT SUCH A GOOD IDEA,

09:51.759 --> 09:53.629
WITH YOUR COMPANY BEING
TAKEN OVER?

09:53.661 --> 09:55.631
- THEY NEED ME
MORE THAN I NEED THEM.

09:55.663 --> 09:57.973
- GUESS YOU'VE GOT
BIGGER BALLS THAN I DO.

09:57.998 --> 10:00.768
- WAS IT EVER A QUESTION?

10:00.801 --> 10:03.741
- WHAT'LL IT BE, BOYS?
DRINKS ARE ON ME.

10:03.771 --> 10:04.841
- IS THAT WHAT YOU'RE GONNA DO

10:04.872 --> 10:06.972
WITH THE 100 BUCKS
I GAVE YOU?

10:07.007 --> 10:10.737
- I, UH, WON'T BE NEEDING ANY
FURTHER FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE.

10:12.312 --> 10:14.652
- SOMEBODY
ACCIDENTALLY DEPOSITED

10:14.682 --> 10:18.322
$10 MILLION IN HIS ACCOUNT.

10:18.351 --> 10:21.391
- FUCK!

10:21.421 --> 10:24.021
- I HOPE YOU DIDN'T TOUCH
ANY OF IT.

10:24.057 --> 10:26.857
- JUST A MEASLY 300.

10:26.894 --> 10:28.264
- WHAT?

10:28.295 --> 10:30.425
DO YOU REALIZE
WHAT YOU'VE DONE?

10:30.463 --> 10:31.973
YOU COMMITTED BANK FRAUD.

10:31.999 --> 10:33.169
THAT'S A FEDERAL OFFENSE.

10:33.200 --> 10:36.270
- OH--OH, MY GOD.
- I WARNED YOU.

10:36.303 --> 10:38.943
- OH, MY GOD,
WHAT AM I GONNA DO?

10:38.972 --> 10:40.112
- TOMORROW YOU'RE GONNA
GO BACK TO THE BANK,

10:40.140 --> 10:42.640
YOU'RE GONNA RETURN
EVERY CENT.

10:45.979 --> 10:48.879
- UH, DO YOU MIND IF
I BORROW BACK THAT 100?

10:48.916 --> 10:51.846
THERE WAS THIS
FABULOUS GUCCI BELT.

11:08.268 --> 11:11.808
- AH.

11:11.839 --> 11:13.039
GARDNER VANCE.

11:13.073 --> 11:15.043
- BRIAN KINNEY.
- SIT.

