11:31.058 --> 11:33.228
- WHICH IS WHY I FIRED
EVERYONE ELSE.

11:33.260 --> 11:37.930
- I'VE ALWAYS HATED THOSE LONG
LINES AT THE WATER COOLER.

11:37.965 --> 11:42.065
- HE ALSO TELLS ME
THAT YOU ARE ARROGANT,

11:42.102 --> 11:46.442
WILLFUL, AND, UM,
INSUBORDINATE.

11:48.308 --> 11:50.778
- I'LL TRY MY BEST TO LIVE UP
TO MY REPUTATION.

11:50.811 --> 11:52.051
- WHY DON'T YOU START
BY TELLING ME

11:52.079 --> 11:54.349
WHY I SHOULDN'T FIRE YOU TOO?

11:58.852 --> 12:00.152
- FOR ONE THING,

12:00.187 --> 12:03.417
