THIS COMPANY THAN YOU DO.

12:03.456 --> 12:05.956
FOR ANOTHER, I HAVE THE
RELATIONSHIP WITH THE CLIENTS.

12:05.993 --> 12:08.063
IF I GO, THEY GO.

12:08.095 --> 12:10.525
