YOU'RE GONNA GET MORE OUT OF ME

12:10.563 --> 12:15.873
THAN SOME TALENTLESS TOADY
YOU BRING IN FOR HALF THE PRICE.

12:15.903 --> 12:17.403
- BEFORE I ACQUIRED THIS FIRM,

12:17.437 --> 12:20.267
