EVERYTHING.

12:20.307 --> 12:23.207
I ALSO CONTACTED EVERY ONE
OF YOUR CLIENTS,

12:23.243 --> 12:27.453
AND THEY AGREED TO STAY,
WITH OR WITHOUT YOU.

12:27.480 --> 12:30.850
WITH REGARD TO
MY HIRING SOME "TOADY,"

12:30.884 --> 12:33.294
