THING I DOUBT YOU EVER WILL--

12:33.320 --> 12:34.350
THEIR LOYALTY.

12:34.387 --> 12:36.387
SO ARE THERE
ANY OTHER REASONS

12:36.423 --> 12:39.063
WHY I SHOULDN'T
FIRE YOU TOO?

12:42.195 --> 12:43.925
- I CAN'T THINK OF ONE.

12:46.466 --> 12:49.236
- YOU'VE GOT A WEEK.

12:49.269 --> 12:53.369
PROVE TO ME
THAT YOU'RE WORTH IT.

12:53.406 --> 12:55.476
- THAT LONG?

12:55.508 --> 12:57.538
- OH, BY THE WAY,

12:57.577 --> 13:01.407
