13:01.448 --> 13:03.948
- THE RUMOR'S RIGHT.

13:03.984 --> 13:08.294
BUT UNLESS I'M FUCKING YOU,
IT'S NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.

13:09.622 --> 13:11.562
- THERE'S BEEN
A SLIGHT MISUNDERSTANDING.

13:11.591 --> 13:12.861
- VERY SLIGHT.

13:12.893 --> 13:14.963
- TINY.
ITSY-BITSY-WEENSY.

13:14.995 --> 13:17.595
- YEAH, IT SEEMS
MR. HONEYCUTT INADVERTENTLY

13:17.630 --> 13:19.470
