HAVE A NICE DAY.

13:23.403 --> 13:26.913
- WAIT RIGHT THERE.

13:26.940 --> 13:29.040
- OH MY GOD.
THEY'RE GONNA ARREST ME.

13:29.076 --> 13:30.106
- ALL RIGHT,
JUST CALM DOWN.

13:30.143 --> 13:32.553
- WHAT AM I GONNA DO?
- YOU'RE GONNA PLAY DUMB.

13:32.579 --> 13:33.979
- I CAN DO THAT.

13:34.014 --> 13:35.324
- YOU'RE GONNA SAY
YOU WITHDREW THE MONEY,

13:35.348 --> 13:36.578
NEVER REALIZING
IT WASN'T YOURS,

13:36.616 --> 13:38.246
WHICH IS WHY YOU'VE
COME TO RETURN IT.

13:38.285 --> 13:40.145
- THAT'S PERFECT.
THAT'S PERFECT.

13:40.187 --> 13:41.387
THEY'RE SURE
TO BELIEVE ME.

13:41.421 --> 13:44.391
- BUT IF THEY DON'T, TRY FOR
A CELL WITH SOUTHERN EXPOSURE.

13:44.424 --> 13:46.434
- WHICH ONE OF YOU
IS MR. HONEYCUTT?

13:46.459 --> 13:48.429
- I-I-I--

13:48.461 --> 13:49.461
- HE IS.

13:49.496 --> 13:51.926
- PLEASE COME WITH ME.

13:51.965 --> 13:54.865
- I DID IT.
I STOLE THE MONEY.

13:54.902 --> 13:56.242
I'M GUILTY.

13:56.269 --> 13:58.139
I'M SO, SO SORRY.

13:58.171 --> 14:00.111
[sobbing]

14:00.140 --> 14:02.010
- IT WAS A MISTAKE.

14:02.042 --> 14:04.182
- OH, IT WAS NO MISTAKE.

14:04.211 --> 14:07.051
THE MONEY WAS CORRECTLY
DEPOSITED INTO YOUR ACCOUNT,

14:07.080 --> 14:08.980
ALL $10 MILLION OF IT.

14:12.385 --> 14:17.385
- I NEED TO, UH,
CONSULT WITH MY ACCOUNTANT.

14:17.424 --> 14:19.964
WHAT EXACTLY DID HE MEAN
BY THAT?

14:25.298 --> 14:27.598
- WHAT EXACTLY
DID YOU MEAN BY THAT?

14:27.634 --> 14:30.504
- THE MONEY WAS LEFT TO YOU
BY GEORGE SCHICKEL.

14:30.537 --> 14:32.507
- GEORGE?

14:32.539 --> 14:35.879
- HE ALSO WANTED YOU
TO HAVE THIS.

14:45.585 --> 14:48.455
- FIND ANYTHING?

14:48.488 --> 14:50.658
- GARDNER VANCE, 41,

14:50.690 --> 14:52.330
GRADUATED HARVARD
BUSINESS SCHOOL,

14:52.359 --> 14:55.599
STARTED AS A COPYWRITER
FOR D.B.D. & O. IN NEW YORK,

14:55.628 --> 14:59.028
THEN JUNIOR AD EXEC AT I & R
IN CHICAGO,

14:59.066 --> 15:02.296
PARTNER AT W.J. IN L.A.

15:02.335 --> 15:03.465
WHAT ABOUT YOU?

15:03.503 --> 15:04.643
WHAT DID YOU FIND?

15:04.671 --> 15:07.141
- UH, MOSTLY THE SAME AS YOU,

15:07.174 --> 15:09.484
PLUS A FEATURE ARTICLE
THEY DID ON HIM

15:09.509 --> 15:13.349
IN ONE OF THE CHICAGO PAPERS.

15:13.380 --> 15:14.680
- DIVORCED TWICE.

15:14.714 --> 15:16.184
BOXING FANATIC.

15:16.216 --> 15:18.086
WOW!
STRAIGHT GUYS.

15:18.118 --> 15:19.488
- WELL, THERE'S AN INTERESTING
QUOTE THOUGH.

15:19.519 --> 15:23.019
I CIRCLED IT.

15:23.056 --> 15:25.286
- "WHEN ASKED IF THERE WAS
AN ACCOUNT HE'D NEVER BEEN

15:25.325 --> 15:27.355
"ABLE TO LAND VANCE SAID,

15:27.394 --> 15:31.604
'YEAH, BROWN ATHLETICS.'"

15:40.340 --> 15:41.710
- WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

15:41.741 --> 15:44.041
- TO SEE A FEW
OF MY HOTTEST TRICKS.

15:44.077 --> 15:45.647
- YOU'RE GOING
TO THE BATHS NOW?

15:45.678 --> 15:48.648
YOU'RE GONNA FUCK US BOTH
OUT OF A JOB.

15:50.483 --> 15:54.223
- THIS IS THE FILTHIEST,

15:54.254 --> 15:58.164
THE SLEAZIEST, MOST DISGUSTING
MOTEL ROOM I'VE EVER SEEN.

15:58.191 --> 16:01.161
- YOU WERE EXPECTING
THE RITZ-CARLTON?

16:01.194 --> 16:03.734
- UH-HUH.

16:03.763 --> 16:05.373
- WHAT, HEY,
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

16:05.398 --> 16:07.468
- HOME.
- BUT WE JUST WALKED IN.

16:07.500 --> 16:09.200
- AND NOW WE'RE
JUST WALKING OUT.

16:09.236 --> 16:11.436
- BUT WE ALREADY PAID.
- BY THE HOUR.

16:11.471 --> 16:13.741
WHAT KIND OF MOTEL
HAS HOURLY RATES?

16:13.773 --> 16:16.013
- THE KIND WHERE
YOU SNEAK AWAY

16:16.043 --> 16:17.543
FOR A QUICKIE
WITH SOME CHICKIE

16:17.577 --> 16:20.107
AND HOPE YOUR WIFE
DOESN'T FIND OUT.

16:24.351 --> 16:26.491
TAKE OFF YOUR COAT.
STAY A WHILE.

16:26.519 --> 16:28.659
- [groans]

16:32.325 --> 16:35.095
BUT THERE ARE STAINS
ON THE BEDSPREAD.

16:35.128 --> 16:38.228
AND HOLES IN THE CARPET,
AND IT SMELLS.

16:38.265 --> 16:40.625
- WHEW, I KNOW.

16:40.667 --> 16:44.637
SLEAZY, SEXY,
SPONTANEOUS.

16:48.075 --> 16:50.205
- CAN'T WE
BE SPONTANEOUS SOME--

16:50.243 --> 16:52.713
SOMEPLACE ELSE LIKE WHERE
THEY CHANGE THE SHEETS,

16:52.745 --> 16:56.045
AND HAVE ROOM SERVICE?

16:56.083 --> 16:58.453
- THIS SAYS THEY HAVE
A COMPLETE LINE OF SEX TOYS,

16:58.485 --> 17:02.415
INCLUDING 31 FLAVORS OF
LUBRICANT AT THE FRONT DESK.

17:02.455 --> 17:03.815
TAKE YOUR PICK.

17:03.856 --> 17:06.256
[both chuckle]

17:14.666 --> 17:16.797
COME ON.

17:32.585 --> 17:35.485
THAT'S A GOOD GIRL.

17:50.370 --> 17:52.410
[muffled pounding]

17:52.439 --> 17:53.439
[muffled moaning]

17:53.473 --> 17:56.413
- JESUS CHRIST!

17:56.443 --> 17:59.653
- HARDER, HARDER.
HARDER, HARDER.

17:59.679 --> 18:00.649
[moaning]

18:00.680 --> 18:02.380
- I GOTTA CALL THE MANAGER.

18:02.415 --> 18:05.615
- IT'S NOT THE RITZ-CARLTON.

18:05.652 --> 18:07.522
WHY DON'T WE PUT THE TV ON?

18:07.554 --> 18:10.224
MAYBE IT'LL DROWN THEM OUT.

18:11.624 --> 18:14.464
- WHAT ELSE IS ON?

18:14.494 --> 18:16.564
UGH.

18:16.596 --> 18:19.866
- [indistinct]

18:19.899 --> 18:21.329
- NO, IT'S NOT.

18:21.368 --> 18:23.898
- THOSE THINGS AREN'T REAL,
ARE THEY?

18:23.936 --> 18:25.866
- I HOPE NOT.

18:25.905 --> 18:28.575
- [indistinct]

18:28.608 --> 18:29.578
- WOW.

18:29.609 --> 18:31.439
- [moaning]

18:31.478 --> 18:33.348
- INVENTED IN BEIJING,
AS THE CHINESE...

18:33.380 --> 18:36.580
- OH! IT'S MY FAVORITE
COOKING SHOW.

18:36.616 --> 18:38.846
HE'S PREPARING
MANDARIN DUCK.

18:38.885 --> 18:41.215
I'VE ALWAYS WANTED
TO KNOW HOW TO MAKE THAT.

18:41.254 --> 18:42.394
- THIS IS AN AIR PUMP.

18:42.422 --> 18:44.422
IT'S ACTUALLY GONNA PUMP
AIR INTO IT,

18:44.457 --> 18:46.457
SEPARATES THE SKIN
FROM THE MEAT,

18:46.493 --> 18:48.263
AND THAT'S THE SECRET
OF RENDERING OFF THE FAT.

18:48.295 --> 18:49.755
ONCE IT'S SEPARATED...

18:49.796 --> 18:51.796
- HEY, EMMETT.

18:51.831 --> 18:54.601
- HI, GEORGE.

18:54.634 --> 18:57.604
- I MISS YOU.

18:57.637 --> 18:59.767
I MISS YOU TOO.

18:59.806 --> 19:03.606
- NOW YOU MUSTN'T CRY.

19:03.643 --> 19:05.183
- I'LL TRY NOT TO.

19:05.212 --> 19:07.212
- LET ME SEE YOU SMILE NOW.

19:07.247 --> 19:09.847
- I DON'T KNOW IF I CAN.

19:09.882 --> 19:14.322
- EMMETT, NOW COME ON.
YOU CAN DO BETTER THAN THAT.

19:14.354 --> 19:16.194
THAT'S BETTER.

19:16.223 --> 19:19.593
WELL, DID YOU RECEIVE
MY LITTLE GIFT?

19:19.626 --> 19:21.556
- "LITTLE"?

19:21.594 --> 19:23.234
GOD, I COULDN'T BELIEVE IT.

19:23.263 --> 19:24.263
- NEITHER COULD WE.

19:24.297 --> 19:26.267
- SEE, YOU--YOU ALWAYS SAY,

19:26.299 --> 19:27.799
"FUCK 'EM ALL."

19:27.834 --> 19:32.244
WELL, TO DO THAT YOU'VE GOT
TO HAVE "FUCK 'EM ALL" MONEY.

19:32.272 --> 19:35.442
- WELL, WHAT AM I SUPPOSED
TO DO WITH IT?

19:35.475 --> 19:36.635
- WHATEVER YOU WANT.

19:36.676 --> 19:38.746
WHATEVER MAKES YOU HAPPY.

19:38.778 --> 19:41.578
- YOU MADE ME HAPPY.

19:41.614 --> 19:43.624
- YOU TOO.

19:43.650 --> 19:45.750
MORE THAN YOU'LL KNOW.

19:45.785 --> 19:48.685
- 10 MIL'S A PRETTY
CLEAR INDICATION.

19:48.721 --> 19:50.891
- WELL, I--

19:50.923 --> 19:53.433
I GUESS THIS IS IT.

19:53.460 --> 19:55.430
YOU'RE OFF ON YOUR ADVENTURE.

19:55.462 --> 19:58.432
I'M OFF ON MINE.

20:21.621 --> 20:23.721
- I NEED THESE IN THREE HOURS.

20:23.756 --> 20:26.726
- I'M NOT FOTOMAT.

20:26.759 --> 20:28.999
I'LL TRY.

20:29.028 --> 20:33.598
*

20:33.633 --> 20:34.973
THAT'S GOOD.

20:35.001 --> 20:39.911
*

20:39.939 --> 20:42.579
DIP IN HERE.

20:42.609 --> 20:43.679
*

20:43.710 --> 20:45.310
THANK YOU.

20:45.345 --> 20:47.375
- * WHAT CAN YOU SEE
WITH YOUR NAKED EYE *

20:47.414 --> 20:50.324
* GIVE ME ONE MORE SHOT

20:50.350 --> 20:52.350
* TO SHOW YOU WHAT I'VE GOT

20:52.385 --> 20:54.815
- GOOD.

20:54.854 --> 20:57.524
- * SEE ME

20:57.557 --> 20:58.827
- NICE, GUYS.

20:58.858 --> 20:59.828
BEAUTIFUL!

20:59.859 --> 21:02.059
YES, PERFECT.

21:02.094 --> 21:05.904
*

21:07.534 --> 21:08.504
YEAH, GOOD.

21:08.535 --> 21:10.465
- GOT YOUR AIRLINE TICKET.

21:10.503 --> 21:13.913
I DON'T THINK
YOU'LL BE NEEDING IT.

21:13.940 --> 21:15.780
CALLED BROWN'S OFFICE.

21:15.808 --> 21:18.778
THEY SAID HE DOESN'T ACCEPT
UNSOLICITED PITCHES.

21:18.811 --> 21:20.981
- YEAH, YEAH, GOOD.

21:21.013 --> 21:23.553
- DO YOU WANT ME TO CANCEL?

21:27.354 --> 21:28.624
- TA-DA.

21:28.655 --> 21:30.485
- OH, EMMETT!

21:30.523 --> 21:31.963
[laughing]

21:31.991 --> 21:35.601
YOU CAN'T DO THIS.

21:35.628 --> 21:37.898
- GOD, PEOPLE DON'T GET
THEIR FRIENDS A CAR.

21:37.930 --> 21:39.770
- UNLESS YOU'RE
A GAME SHOW HOST.

21:39.799 --> 21:41.029
- OH, IT'S NOT JUST A CAR.

21:41.067 --> 21:42.937
IT'S A SUBARU SUV.

21:42.969 --> 21:45.369
- [cheering]

21:45.405 --> 21:47.535
- I READ IN A RECENT SURVEY,

21:47.574 --> 21:48.914
IT'S THE NUMBER ONE CHOICE
AMONG LESBIANS.

21:48.941 --> 21:50.981
I'M SURE MR. SUBARU
WOULD BE THRILLED.

21:53.145 --> 21:57.015
- UM, JUSTIN,
THIS IS FOR YOU.

21:57.049 --> 21:58.389
- A TRIP TO ITALY?

21:58.418 --> 21:59.348
- YEAH.

21:59.386 --> 22:02.616
GEORGE AND I WERE PLANNING,
BUT NEVER MIND.

22:02.655 --> 22:05.385
YOU'RE GOING, AS ARTISTS
HAVE FOR CENTURIES,

22:05.425 --> 22:08.085
TO THE ETERNAL CITY,
TO FLORENCE, TO VENICE.

22:08.127 --> 22:11.357
IT IS THERE THAT YOU WILL
DISCOVER YOUR SOUL.

22:11.398 --> 22:13.968
- AND SEE LOTS OF
STATUES OF NAKED MEN TOO.

22:14.000 --> 22:16.770
- THANKS, EM.

22:16.803 --> 22:18.143
- AND WHEN YOU AND BRIAN
ARE IN MILAN,

22:18.170 --> 22:20.440
HE CAN USE THIS.

22:20.473 --> 22:21.713
IT'S A GIFT CERTIFICATE

22:21.741 --> 22:23.841
TO ARMANI FOR
THE FALL COLLECTION.

22:23.876 --> 22:25.446
- OH, HE'LL LOVE A NEW SUIT.

22:25.478 --> 22:26.878
- THE ENTIRE COLLECTION.

22:26.913 --> 22:28.553
[laughter]

22:28.581 --> 22:29.981
HE'LL NEVER WONDER
WHAT TO WEAR AGAIN.

22:30.016 --> 22:30.976
[laughter]

22:31.017 --> 22:33.117
AND, DEBBIE,

22:33.152 --> 22:35.862
FOR YOU.

22:35.888 --> 22:37.988
- OH SHIT,
YOU'RE GONNA MAKE ME CRY.

22:38.024 --> 22:39.064
NO.

22:39.091 --> 22:40.461
- OH MY GOD.

22:40.493 --> 22:42.463
- OH, MA.

22:42.495 --> 22:44.025
- OH.
- WOW.

22:44.063 --> 22:45.833
- NO, EMMETT.
NO. I COULDN'T.

22:45.865 --> 22:47.125
- YEAH!

22:47.166 --> 22:50.496
NOW WHEN YOU ARE
SLINGING THAT HASH,

22:50.537 --> 22:55.007
EVERYONE WILL THINK
YOU'RE A PRINCESS.

22:55.041 --> 22:57.441
- THANK YOU.

22:57.477 --> 23:01.807
MICHAEL.
[chuckles]

23:05.918 --> 23:08.818
- JESUS, EM.

23:08.855 --> 23:11.585
HE PAID THE MORTGAGE
ON MY COMIC BOOK STORE

23:11.624 --> 23:13.694
FOR THE NEXT FIVE YEARS.

23:13.726 --> 23:14.856
- OH, HONEY.

23:14.894 --> 23:16.764
- YOU JUST CHANGED MY LIFE.

23:16.796 --> 23:19.696
[laughter]

23:19.732 --> 23:24.542
- OH, GUESS THERE'S NOTHING
IN THE BAG FOR ME.

23:24.571 --> 23:25.571
- HMM.

23:25.605 --> 23:26.965
[mumbling]

23:27.006 --> 23:27.966
OH!

23:28.007 --> 23:30.537
both: OHH!

23:30.577 --> 23:32.107
- THE ONE PRESENT
I REALLY WANTED TO GET YOU,

23:32.144 --> 23:33.714
I COULDN'T.

23:33.746 --> 23:35.716
SOMEONE WONDERFUL
TO SPEND YOUR LIFE WITH.

23:35.748 --> 23:38.788
- AH, WELL, THERE'S ALWAYS
A GOLDEN RETRIEVER.

23:45.725 --> 23:49.455
LIFETIME ORCHESTRA SEAT
AT THE OPERA.

23:49.496 --> 23:50.956
- TWO LIFETIME SEATS,

23:50.997 --> 23:54.467
'CAUSE I KNOW YOU'LL
FIND THAT SOMEONE.

23:54.501 --> 23:56.541
- THANK YOU.

24:00.907 --> 24:02.577
- WHAT ABOUT YOURSELF,
EMMETT?

24:02.609 --> 24:04.709
- I HOPE YOU GOT YOURSELF
SOMETHING.

24:04.744 --> 24:06.214
- OH, NO. NO.

24:06.245 --> 24:09.515
IT'S MUCH BETTER TO GIVE
THAN TO RECEIVE.

24:09.549 --> 24:10.819
EXCEPT IN BED.

24:10.850 --> 24:11.950
[laughter]

24:11.984 --> 24:14.924
HOWEVER, THERE WAS
A LITTLE SOMETHING

24:14.954 --> 24:16.824
THAT DID CATCH MY EYE.

24:16.856 --> 24:18.086
- HERE WE GO.

24:18.124 --> 24:19.694
- NOW'S WHEN I START TO WORRY.

24:19.726 --> 24:22.996
- GEORGE WANTED IT TO BE
"FUCK 'EM ALL" MONEY.

24:23.029 --> 24:25.569
[cheering]

24:25.598 --> 24:28.638
WELL, GEORGIE,
THEY'LL HEAR ME IN THIS.

24:28.668 --> 24:30.068
HA HA!

24:30.102 --> 24:32.002
[all oohing]

24:32.038 --> 24:34.738
- LIBERACE.

24:44.617 --> 24:45.717
- [startled gasp]

24:45.752 --> 24:46.892
HEY.

24:46.919 --> 24:49.589
I WAS JUST ON MY WAY
TO THE KITCHEN

24:49.622 --> 24:51.222
TO MAKE MYSELF A SANDWICH.

24:51.257 --> 24:53.757
- COME SHARE MINE.
COME ON.

24:56.896 --> 24:59.126
- I DIDN'T EXPECT YOU
TO BE HERE.

24:59.165 --> 25:01.725
I FIGURED YOU'D BE OUT PAINTING
THE TOWN RED OR...

25:01.768 --> 25:05.298
WHATEVER COLOR THEY PAINT
TOWNS THESE DAYS.

25:05.337 --> 25:07.537
- ALL THE HOT GALS ARE
HOME WITH THEIR WIVES,

25:07.574 --> 25:09.684
GETTING IT ON.

25:09.709 --> 25:11.079
HOW ABOUT YOU GUYS?

25:11.110 --> 25:13.280
- WE TRIED GOING TO A MOTEL.

25:13.312 --> 25:15.212
- NO SHIT!

25:15.247 --> 25:16.777
DID THEY HEAR YOU SCREAMING
THROUGH THE WALLS?

25:16.816 --> 25:18.276
- THAT WAS SOMEONE ELSE.

25:18.317 --> 25:21.147
WE WERE THE ONES
WATCHING THE COOKING SHOW.

25:21.187 --> 25:22.687
- WELL, IF I'D BEEN THERE, I'D
HAVE PINNED YOU BOTH TO THE BED

25:22.722 --> 25:23.892
AND DONE THE DOZEN-DOZEN--

25:23.923 --> 25:26.133
12 ORGASMS IN
12 DIFFERENT POSITIONS.

25:26.158 --> 25:27.858
- [coughs]

25:27.894 --> 25:29.864
- YOU OKAY?

25:29.896 --> 25:31.126
- JUST WENT DOWN
THE WRONG WAY.

25:31.163 --> 25:33.203
- CHRIST, YOU'RE TIGHT.

25:33.232 --> 25:35.202
HONEY, YOU NEED TO LOOSEN UP.

25:35.234 --> 25:36.674
LIE DOWN.

25:36.703 --> 25:38.173
- NO, NO, NO, NO.
IT'S OKAY, IT'S OKAY.

25:38.204 --> 25:39.974
- NO, NO, I'M JUST GONNA
RUB YOUR SHOULDERS.

25:40.006 --> 25:41.906
MM-HMM.

25:41.941 --> 25:44.541
COME ON. COME ON.

25:47.113 --> 25:49.723
I'LL GET ALL
THE STRESS WORKED OUT.

25:49.749 --> 25:53.289
AND THEN YOU AND THE MISSUS
CAN SPONTANEOUSLY COMBUST.

25:55.788 --> 25:57.058
MMM.

25:57.089 --> 25:58.959
YOU KNOW WHAT YOU NEED?

25:58.991 --> 26:00.931
SHIATSU.

26:00.960 --> 26:02.930
- HMM.
MM-HMM.

26:02.962 --> 26:05.632
- OR EVEN BETTER,

26:05.665 --> 26:07.825
TANTRIC.

26:11.671 --> 26:14.811
HAVE YOU EVER HAD
A DEEP RECTAL MASSAGE?

26:14.841 --> 26:16.841
- NOT RECENTLY.

26:16.876 --> 26:18.876
- YOU HAVE NO IDEA
HOW MUCH TENSION

26:18.911 --> 26:22.721
PEOPLE CARRY
IN THEIR SPHINCTERS.

26:22.749 --> 26:24.879
[both chuckle]

26:27.987 --> 26:29.757
SHH.

26:29.789 --> 26:33.159
[laughter]

26:33.192 --> 26:34.932
- EMMETT GOT EVERYONE
THE COOLEST STUFF.

26:34.961 --> 26:36.361
HE GOT CARS, TRIPS.

26:36.395 --> 26:38.095
HE EVEN GAVE DEBBIE
A DIAMOND BRACELET.

26:38.130 --> 26:40.230
- I REALLY HAVE
TO HAND IT TO HIM.

26:40.266 --> 26:42.636
HE MUST HAVE GIVEN GEORGE
ONE HELL OF A BLOW JOB.

26:42.669 --> 26:43.999
HAVE YOU SEEN MY PRADA TIE?

26:44.036 --> 26:44.996
- FUCK THE TIE.

26:45.037 --> 26:47.807
HE GOT YOU THE ENTIRE
ARMANI FALL COLLECTION.

26:47.840 --> 26:49.380
- YEAH, WELL, WHAT AM I
SUPPOSED TO WEAR UNTIL THEN?

26:49.408 --> 26:51.708
- HE GOT ME A TRIP TO ITALY

26:51.744 --> 26:53.114
TO SEE ALL THE MASTERS.

26:53.145 --> 26:56.375
- YEAH, I HEARD THEY HAVE
A BIG S&M SCENE THERE.

26:56.415 --> 26:59.215
- WHY ARE YOU BRINGING A TIE
TO GO SNOWBOARDING?

26:59.251 --> 27:02.321
- I'M NOT GOING SNOWBOARDING.

27:02.354 --> 27:03.994
I'M GOING TO CHICAGO.

27:04.023 --> 27:05.793
- CHICAGO?

27:05.825 --> 27:07.125
WHAT THE HELL'S IN CHICAGO?

27:07.159 --> 27:09.129
- MY NEW ACCOUNT.

27:09.161 --> 27:12.101
- BUT WE'RE GOING
TO VERMONT TOMORROW.

27:12.131 --> 27:13.201
- SOME OTHER TIME.

27:13.232 --> 27:16.842
- COME ON, YOU PROMISED.

27:16.869 --> 27:17.939
- IT'S BUSINESS.

27:17.970 --> 27:19.410
- FUCK BUSINESS!

27:19.438 --> 27:23.738
- THAT'S EXACTLY
WHO YOU'RE FUCKING.

27:23.776 --> 27:24.976
IT'S BUSINESS.

27:25.011 --> 27:27.011
IT'S MY BUSINESS.

27:27.046 --> 27:29.276
IT PAYS FOR THIS LOFT.

27:29.315 --> 27:31.775
IT PAYS FOR SNOWBOARDING
IN VERMONT.

27:31.818 --> 27:34.688
IT PAYS FOR THE PITTSBURGH
INSTITUTE OF FINE ARTS.

27:34.721 --> 27:36.991
NOW, IF I DON'T
GET ON THAT PLANE,

27:37.023 --> 27:39.293
I'M GOING TO BE
COLLECTING UNEMPLOYMENT

27:39.325 --> 27:41.985
IN MY FUCKING ARMANI
FALL COLLECTION.

28:02.081 --> 28:06.051
- HEY, SWEETS.
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

28:06.085 --> 28:08.755
- LOOKS GREAT.

28:08.788 --> 28:11.058
- LINDSAY'S ALL HEPPED TOO.

28:11.090 --> 28:13.790
- YOU'VE DONE AN AMAZING JOB.

28:13.826 --> 28:14.826
- THANKS.

28:14.861 --> 28:17.931
- WHOA, CAREFUL.

28:17.964 --> 28:21.474
SHE AND I ARE
ETERNALLY GRATEFUL.

28:21.500 --> 28:23.440
- ANYTHING FOR YOU GUYS,
YOU KNOW THAT.

28:23.469 --> 28:25.199
- BUT, YOU KNOW,
IT'S NOT FAIR

28:25.237 --> 28:27.867
ASKING YOU TO DO ALL THIS
BY YOURSELF.

28:27.907 --> 28:29.277
- I'M LOVING IT.

28:29.308 --> 28:31.408
- NO, REALLY, I MEAN,
IT'S TOO BIG A JOB.

28:31.443 --> 28:34.183
WE CAN FIND A CARPENTER
OR A HANDYMAN

28:34.213 --> 28:36.883
TO COME IN AND FINISH IT UP.

28:36.916 --> 28:38.986
- SUGAR, THERE'S
NO HANDYMAN OR WOMAN

28:39.018 --> 28:40.188
HANDIER THAN ME.

28:40.219 --> 28:44.059
- I KNOW ALL ABOUT
YOUR HANDIWORK.

28:44.090 --> 28:46.330
LIKE THE JOB YOU WERE DOING
ON LINDSAY LAST NIGHT.

28:46.358 --> 28:48.898
- THAT WAS JUST A FRIENDLY
LITTLE MASSAGE.

28:48.928 --> 28:50.428
- [scoffs]

28:50.462 --> 28:53.502
IT LOOKED MORE THAN
A LITTLE FRIENDLY TO ME.

28:53.532 --> 28:57.442
- JESUS, WHAT'S WITH
THE JEALOUS WIFE ROUTINE?

28:57.469 --> 28:59.369
- I MASSAGE HER AND
SHE FUCKING FALLS ASLEEP.

28:59.405 --> 29:01.135
YOU RUB HER AND SHE PURRS.

29:01.173 --> 29:03.983
- OH, SO NOW I'M TO BLAME
FOR YOUR LESBIAN BED DEATH.

29:04.010 --> 29:06.510
- ALL I KNOW IS EVERYTHING
WAS FINE BEFORE YOU MOVED IN.

29:06.545 --> 29:07.975
- WHO THE HELL INVITED ME?

29:08.014 --> 29:10.124
- I DID.

29:10.149 --> 29:13.289
AND NOW I'M ASKING YOU
TO LEAVE.

29:19.291 --> 29:21.091
- YOU WANT SOME?

29:21.127 --> 29:22.857
- NOT HUNGRY.

29:22.895 --> 29:24.955
- WHAT ARE YOU TRYING TO DO,
STARVE YOURSELF TO DEATH?

29:24.997 --> 29:26.397
- YOU SOUND JUST LIKE DEB.

29:26.432 --> 29:29.102
- I WONDER HOW THAT HAPPENED.

29:29.135 --> 29:31.995
COME ON, EAT.

29:32.038 --> 29:34.138
YOU WANT TO HEAR
MY SECRET FANTASY?

29:34.173 --> 29:36.013
- I DON'T GENERALLY LIKE
DISCUSSING KINK

29:36.042 --> 29:37.042
ON AN EMPTY STOMACH.

29:37.076 --> 29:40.276
- TO SEE RAGE
ON A CEREAL BOX,

29:40.312 --> 29:41.982
PREFERABLY FROOT LOOPS.

29:42.014 --> 29:43.554
A LITTLE ACTION FIGURE INSIDE.

29:43.582 --> 29:45.052
- COLLECT ALL THREE.

29:45.084 --> 29:46.594
- COULD HAPPEN.
ANYTHING'S POSSIBLE.

29:46.618 --> 29:49.858
- EXCEPT BRIAN AND I ACTUALLY
SPENDING ANY TIME TOGETHER.

29:49.889 --> 29:51.519
- I'M SURE HE WOULD HAVE
RATHER GONE WITH YOU.

29:51.557 --> 29:53.087
HE HAD NO CHOICE.

29:53.125 --> 29:54.555
- DO YOU ALWAYS DEFEND HIM?

29:54.593 --> 29:57.133
- LOOK, IF HE DOESN'T MAKE IT
NOW, HE NEVER WILL.

29:57.163 --> 29:58.363
- HE'S ALREADY MADE IT.

29:58.397 --> 30:00.497
HE HAS MONEY, SUCCESS,
A KILLER LOFT.

30:00.532 --> 30:01.532
WHAT ELSE DOES HE WANT?

30:01.567 --> 30:03.067
- TO BE THE BEST.

30:03.102 --> 30:05.302
IF HE GETS THIS ACCOUNT,
HE'LL BE A STAR.

30:05.337 --> 30:07.137
AND IF HE DOESN'T,
HE'S OUT OF A JOB.

30:07.173 --> 30:09.943
IT WON'T BE THAT EASY
STARTING OVER AT A NEW FIRM.

30:09.976 --> 30:12.136
YOU KNOW, WITH ALL
THESE NEW GUYS,

30:12.178 --> 30:14.048
YOUNGER GUYS,
COMING UP ALL THE TIME.

30:14.080 --> 30:16.150
- SO WHAT ABOUT ME?

30:16.182 --> 30:20.552
WHERE DO I FIT IN?

30:20.586 --> 30:25.586
I DON'T WANT TO WAIT.

30:25.624 --> 30:28.934
I WANT A BOYFRIEND WHO ONLY
WANTS TO BE WITH ME,

30:28.961 --> 30:32.261
WHO WANTS TO STAY HOME
EVERY ONCE IN A WHILE.

30:32.298 --> 30:34.928
WHO AT LEAST GETS JEALOUS WHEN
SOME OTHER GUY'S SUCKING MY DICK

30:34.967 --> 30:36.137
RIGHT IN FRONT OF HIM.

30:36.168 --> 30:39.208
- THAT'S NOT BRIAN.

30:39.238 --> 30:41.508
IT NEVER WILL BE.

30:44.476 --> 30:46.176
- I'M SORRY, MR. KINNEY,

30:46.212 --> 30:47.912
BUT WE LEFT WORD
WITH YOUR ASSISTANT

30:47.947 --> 30:50.077
THAT MR. BROWN WASN'T INTERESTED
IN MEETING WITH YOU.

30:50.116 --> 30:53.146
- TELL HIM I FLEW ALL THE WAY
FROM PITTSBURGH JUST TO SEE HIM.

30:53.185 --> 30:55.185
- UNFORTUNATELY, HE'S IN
A CLOSED- DOOR MEETING

30:55.221 --> 30:56.491
AND CAN'T BE DISTURBED.

30:56.522 --> 30:58.092
- I'LL WAIT.

30:58.124 --> 31:02.494
- HIS DAY IS BOOKED SOLID.

31:02.528 --> 31:04.498
- YOU KNOW, I'M SURE IF HE
SAW MY PRESENTATION--

31:04.530 --> 31:06.630
- LOOK, I'M TRYING TO TELL YOU
THAT YOU'RE WASTING YOUR TIME.

31:06.665 --> 31:08.895
- NO, YOU'RE WASTING HIS TIME,

31:08.935 --> 31:11.265
BECAUSE THE SOONER
YOU GET ME IN TO SEE HIM,

31:11.303 --> 31:14.543
THE SOONER I CAN
SHOW HIM THESE.

31:21.147 --> 31:22.547
- INTERESTING.

31:22.581 --> 31:25.581
- I CAN SEE YOU'RE
IMPRESSED.

31:25.617 --> 31:30.017
MAYBE YOU'D LIKE
A COPY FOR YOURSELF.

31:36.963 --> 31:39.673
- [grunting]

31:39.698 --> 31:42.098
MR. BROWN...UH...

31:42.134 --> 31:43.204
EATS LUNCH...

31:43.235 --> 31:46.265
HARVARD CLUB.

32:10.229 --> 32:11.629
- WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?

32:11.663 --> 32:13.673
- BRIAN KINNEY,
VANGUARD ADVERTISING.

32:13.699 --> 32:15.299
YOUR ASSISTANT
SAID I'D FIND YOU HERE.

32:15.334 --> 32:18.344
- I TOLD HIM TO TELL YOU
I WASN'T INTERESTED.

32:18.370 --> 32:20.970
- REALLY.
WONDER WHAT GOT INTO HIM.

32:21.007 --> 32:22.977
- HERMAN, WILL YOU KINDLY
SHOW THIS GENTLEMAN OUT?

32:23.009 --> 32:26.079
- HERMAN, WOULD YOU KINDLY
BRING US A BOTTLE OF DOM?

32:26.112 --> 32:28.352
ON VANGUARD, OF COURSE.
WE'RE CELEBRATING,

32:28.380 --> 32:31.950
BROWN ATHLETICS'
NEW AD CAMPAIGN.

32:36.588 --> 32:38.288
- IF YOU'RE HERE TO CONVINCE ME
TO BE MORE HIP,

32:38.324 --> 32:39.594
YOU'RE WASTING YOUR TIME.

32:39.625 --> 32:41.525
I'LL BE DAMNED IF I MAKE
A PAIR OF SNEAKERS

32:41.560 --> 32:42.760
THAT LIGHT UP
WHEN YOU BOUNCE.

32:42.794 --> 32:45.204
- LEAVE TRENDINESS
TO THE OTHER GUYS.

32:45.231 --> 32:49.101
WHAT YOU SELL IS GOOD OLD
AMERICAN TRADITION,

32:49.135 --> 32:50.735
BUT YOU NEED SOMETHING

32:50.769 --> 32:53.209
WITH MORE HEAT.

32:53.239 --> 32:55.109
- YOUNG MAN,
THERE IS NO HEAT

32:55.141 --> 32:56.681
IN BASEBALL CAPS
AND WINDBREAKERS.

32:56.708 --> 32:58.338
- YOU'RE RIGHT, THERE'S NOT.

32:58.377 --> 33:02.207
BUT IT'S MY JOB TO MAKE
PEOPLE THINK THAT THERE IS.

33:08.187 --> 33:10.087
- "THE ONE THING TO WEAR".

33:10.122 --> 33:12.362
- WE RUN THESE IN ALL
THE TOP-END MAGAZINES.

33:12.391 --> 33:14.491
VANITY FAIR, ESQUIRE, GQ.

33:14.526 --> 33:16.696
WE APPEAL TO WOMEN BECAUSE
THEY DO MOST OF THE SPENDING,

33:16.728 --> 33:22.028
AND TO THE NEW GAY MARKET.

33:30.409 --> 33:33.109
HERMAN, WOULD YOU
BRING ME A STEAK,

33:33.145 --> 33:34.245
MEDIUM-RARE?

33:34.280 --> 33:37.480
- YES, SIR.

33:40.819 --> 33:43.489
- NOTICE HOW
I CALL ATTENTION TO IT

33:43.522 --> 33:45.562
WITHOUT CALLING
ATTENTION TO IT?

33:45.591 --> 33:47.361
IT'S CALLED CLASS.

33:47.393 --> 33:48.393
- GOT ANY ICE?

33:48.427 --> 33:49.527
- WHAT DO YOU CALL THIS?

33:49.561 --> 33:51.061
- FOR MY WATER!

33:51.097 --> 33:52.057
- [chuckles]

33:52.098 --> 33:53.728
- COMING RIGHT UP.

33:53.765 --> 33:55.625
HEY, MR. MONEYBAGS,

33:55.667 --> 33:57.067
WHAT CAN I GET FOR YOU?

33:57.103 --> 33:59.113
- A DOUGHNUT, PLEASE.

33:59.138 --> 34:00.268
- YOU GOT IT.

34:00.306 --> 34:02.266
- BEEN SHOPPING?

34:02.308 --> 34:03.108
- OF COURSE HE HAS.

34:03.142 --> 34:04.442
WHAT ELSE DOES
A FAGGOT OF LEISURE

34:04.476 --> 34:05.676
HAVE TO DO ALL DAY
EXCEPT SHOP?

34:05.711 --> 34:08.581
- TOO MANY PEOPLE,
TOO TIRING, TOO COLD.

34:08.614 --> 34:09.524
- AND COMPLAIN?

34:09.547 --> 34:12.717
- WELL, THERE WERE
A FEW INTERESTING SALES,

34:12.751 --> 34:14.551
BUT, UM, BUT THEN I
REALIZED I DON'T NEED TO BUY

34:14.585 --> 34:15.416
ON SALE ANYMORE.

34:15.454 --> 34:18.164
AND IT ALL SUDDENLY SEEMED
SO EMPTY.

34:18.190 --> 34:20.330
- ONE QUEER DOUGHNUT
ON THE HOUSE.

34:20.359 --> 34:22.129
- THANKS, DEB.

34:22.161 --> 34:24.301
SO I, UH, I BEGAN TO THINK.

34:24.330 --> 34:25.699
- ALWAYS A DANGEROUS SIGN.

34:25.731 --> 34:29.601
- I'VE INHERITED MORE THAN
VAST SUMS OF MONEY.

34:29.635 --> 34:32.094
I'VE INHERITED
RESPONSIBILITY.

34:32.138 --> 34:33.708
I MEAN, I BOUGHT PRESENTS
FOR EVERYONE

34:33.739 --> 34:36.478
EXCEPT FOR THE ONE PERSON
WHO MADE IT POSSIBLE.

34:36.507 --> 34:39.108
GEORGE.

34:39.145 --> 34:40.445
- EM, GEORGE IS DEAD.

34:40.478 --> 34:42.449
- I KNOW.

34:42.481 --> 34:44.321
I MEAN,
I KNOW I CAN'T BUY HIM,

34:44.350 --> 34:46.489
YOU KNOW, A CAR OR A WATCH,
BUT, UH...

34:46.518 --> 34:48.518
I CAN HONOR HIS MEMORY.

34:48.554 --> 34:50.824
- WELL, HE'S ALREADY GOT LOTS
OF THINGS TO HONOR HIS MEMORY.

34:50.856 --> 34:52.786
- A CONCERT HALL.
- AND A PICKLE.

34:52.824 --> 34:54.864
- I WAS THINKING, UH,
MORE ALONG THE LINES

34:54.893 --> 35:00.403
OF THE GEORGE SCHICKEL
HOME FOR GAY AND LESBIAN YOUTH.

35:02.934 --> 35:04.844
- GEORGE SURE KNEW
WHAT HE WAS DOING

35:04.870 --> 35:08.370
WHEN HE GAVE THAT MONEY
TO YOU, HONEY.

35:10.509 --> 35:11.839
HELLO.

35:11.877 --> 35:13.747
GET YOU ANYTHING?

35:13.779 --> 35:15.179
- EMMETT HONEYCUTT?

35:15.214 --> 35:16.724
- I'M EMMETT HONEYCUTT,

35:16.748 --> 35:18.478
BUT I'M NOT ON THE MENU.

35:18.517 --> 35:21.517
- THIS IS FOR YOU.

35:25.224 --> 35:26.434
- WHAT IS IT?

35:26.458 --> 35:28.758
SOMETHING ABOUT
THE SCHICKEL ESTATE.

35:28.794 --> 35:31.764
- LET ME SEE THAT.

35:31.797 --> 35:34.827
YADA-YADA
"TO INFORM YOU THAT..."

35:34.866 --> 35:36.636
YADA-YADA--

35:36.668 --> 35:39.708
- YADA-YADA WHAT?

35:39.738 --> 35:42.568
- THE SCHICKEL FAMILY

35:42.608 --> 35:47.178
IS CONTESTING EMMETT'S
INHERITANCE.

35:47.213 --> 35:49.553
- BUT...

35:49.581 --> 35:51.651
THEY CAN'T DO THAT.
HE LEFT IT TO ME.

35:51.683 --> 35:53.923
- WELL, APPARENTLY THEY THINK
HE SHOULD'VE LEFT IT TO THEM.

35:53.952 --> 35:56.322
THEY'VE FROZEN YOUR ACCOUNT.

35:56.355 --> 35:59.285
- WELL, WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

35:59.325 --> 36:00.555
- IT MEANS MAYBE
YOU SHOULDN'T HAVE

36:00.592 --> 36:02.762
PASSED UP THOSE SALES
QUITE SO QUICKLY.

36:05.564 --> 36:07.674
- YOU TOLD HER TO LEAVE
WITHOUT EVEN ASKING ME?

36:07.699 --> 36:09.539
- YOU NEVER WANTED HER HERE
IN THE FIRST PLACE.

36:09.568 --> 36:10.668
- WELL, I LIKE THAT
SHE'S HERE NOW.

36:10.702 --> 36:11.942
- YEAH, I BET YOU DO.

36:11.970 --> 36:12.870
- SHE'S DOING AN AMAZING JOB.

36:12.904 --> 36:14.874
- AND NOT JUST IN THE ATTIC.
- EXCUSE ME?

36:14.906 --> 36:16.376
- ALL THIS TIME I'M THINKING

36:16.408 --> 36:17.878
THE REASON THAT WE'RE
NOT FEELING VERY SEXUAL

36:17.909 --> 36:19.809
IS BECAUSE WE'RE TOO TIRED,

36:19.845 --> 36:21.405
THAT WE HAVE TOO MUCH
ON OUR MINDS.

36:21.447 --> 36:22.947
I DIDN'T REALIZE WHAT YOU HAVE
ON YOUR MIND WAS HER.

36:22.981 --> 36:24.281
- WELL, THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

36:24.316 --> 36:25.746
- OH, GOD,
DON'T LIE TO ME.

36:25.784 --> 36:27.424
