FOR SEVEN YEARS.

36:27.453 --> 36:29.593
I KNOW YOU.

36:29.621 --> 36:32.621
- SO MAYBE I DO FIND HER...

36:32.658 --> 36:33.758
ATTRACTIVE.

36:38.464 --> 36:39.574
WHAT ABOUT YOU?

36:39.598 --> 36:42.598
- ME?
THAT WAS YEARS AGO.

36:42.634 --> 36:43.744
- NOW WHO'S LYING?

36:43.769 --> 36:44.839
- OH...

36:44.870 --> 36:46.940
- THE MINUTE SHE CAME
ZOOMING BACK INTO YOUR LIFE,

36:46.972 --> 36:48.872
YOU COULDN'T WAIT TO JUMP
ON THE BACK OF HER MOTORCYCLE.

36:48.907 --> 36:53.607
- ALL RIGHT,
SO SHE'S HOT, SO WHAT?

36:53.645 --> 36:55.945
- YOU KNOW, YOU TWO
OUGHT TO HAVE SOMEONE

36:55.981 --> 36:57.581
