36:57.616 --> 36:58.716
YOU CAN HEAR EVERY WORD.

36:58.750 --> 37:01.020
- CHRIST.

37:01.052 --> 37:05.362
- JUST WANTED TO SAY
THAT I'M SORRY FOR ANY GRIEF.

37:16.502 --> 37:18.342
- HEY, LEDA.

37:24.610 --> 37:28.610
