FRIENDS FOR TOO LONG.

37:28.647 --> 37:31.247
- WE DON'T WANT YOU
TO LEAVE LIKE THIS.

37:40.392 --> 37:41.632
- YOU'RE RIGHT.

37:43.395 --> 37:46.365
